K. G. Sakharov replaced him in this post. On September 7, 2001, in honor of the 15th anniversary of the scientific and technical center, the first stage of the technical museum was opened. all over the country. After the French company Renault became a shareholder of AvtoVAZ OJSC, a decision was made to include the scientific and technical center of the plant into the Renault-Nissan global engineering alliance.[62]
Plans
Development plans in the company are associated with further integration with Renault-Nissan.